                                    ܕܒܢܝ̈ܢܫܐ</rubric>
                <note>See <bibl>Add. 14,632<ptr target="http://syriaca.org/manuscript/382"/>, no. <citedRange>60</citedRange></bibl>.</note> <!--JA: Element citedRange requires attribute for Wright's numbering-->
